data.description: Great house with a ton of upgrades, very clean and absolutely ready to move-in. All custom plaster and custom paint makes it very unique. Rich entrance with tiles, columns and balcony. No carpet is this place, all natural stone or real hardwood floor. Kitchen and bathrooms all remodeled with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances. Master suite with good size bedroom and all updated bathroom: New cabinet with double vanity, built in shower, new soaking tub and all new tile floor. Outside, very good size backyard with chicken coop that could stay or could be removed and a nice garden.  Location convenient to I-20.
